{"tid":1962734,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【新冠肺炎】三上悠亞開Live報平安　邀初中生對話展示大姐姐風範","createTime":"2020-04-07T16:12:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-07T16:36:09.000Z","uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a380de9ff8990185718037dd1d56bfaf8e06a793","tid":1962734,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T16:12:24.000Z","msg":"新冠肺炎（COVID-19）肆虐全球，日本疫情亦相當嚴重，繼著名喜劇泰斗志村健染疫病逝後，搞笑女子組合「森三中」42歲團員黑澤宗子日前亦確診。據日本傳媒報道，上月21日出現發燒症狀，未發病前一天更到電視台參與錄製東京電視台節目《麝香葡萄之夜》，與AV女優三上悠亞、桃乃木香奈和架乃由羅等同台演出，令外界擔心日本AV界是否跟着淪陷。正當粉絲擔心一眾女神的情況時，其中之一的三上悠亞便在社交網站直播報平安，疑似正在自我隔離的她與粉絲問好，其間更有與幸運粉絲傾視像電話的環節。最有趣的是，其中一位粉絲是中學生，三上更關心對方留家自習期間有否溫書，好有大姐姐的風範。"},{"pid":"625f7fa61aa8b50fcce15f930e0c18f14e06b7f8","tid":1962734,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T16:12:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4287754/org/91ad9ab6948642741bda4411c5a61d17.jpg/zCeewpNSpgzCBpmX3380eR2SkBh5JU4tHK0yHBytMhw?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4287754%2Forg%2F91ad9ab6948642741bda4411c5a61d17.jpg%2FzCeewpNSpgzCBpmX3380eR2SkBh5JU4tHK0yHBytMhw%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=32dc069c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好想一齊溫書<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67b1439a4eeb2665efc591e066f0b407862eec1b","tid":1962734,"uid":9564,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T16:21:06.000Z","msg":"下邊嗰個睇個頭就知係毒撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8533d94a85558abb9926049acdacd0252f718b5f","tid":1962734,"uid":189109,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T16:21:19.000Z","msg":"一哭二鬧三上悠亞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73a83517cb1f6aff4630f438eff369b058204f82","tid":1962734,"uid":43061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T16:22:42.000Z","msg":"右下愚樂台手足黎<br />\n邊個我就唔講啦"},{"pid":"aff519c9